  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Underground_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - So you followed me down. Good. This is the Underground, where the earth keeps everything that has ever lived.
  - The breath you mastered above will not carry you here. These depths answer only to those who understand what lasts when life is gone.
  - Somewhere in the dark waits the Guardian of the Underground. Find it, and let it judge whether you are ready for the next Fragment, and the power that comes with it.
  - Go. I will not be far.
